<title>Jesus kom inn</title>
<aka>Into my heart</aka>
<key>C</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesus kom inn,
 rens Du mitt sinn.
 Kom inn i mitt hjerte, Jesus.
 Ta bolig der,
 min styrke vær.
 Kom inn i mitt hjerte, Jesus.

[V2]
 Into my heart,
 Into my heart,
 Come into my heart, Lord Jesus.
 Come in today,
 Come in to stay.
 Come into my heart, Lord Jesus!</lyrics>
</song>